BEGIN_PGML Water straight out of the tap is [`[$b]`] degrees Fahrenheit, and you fill a tea kettle. You place the tea kettle on an old stove burner and turn on the burner, but the heating element is old and not working well. At _best_, it begins raising the temperature inside the kettle at a rate of [`[$m]`] degrees Fahrenheit per minute. How long will it take to boil the water? (Water boils at [`212`] degrees Fahrenheit.)
END_PGML
